OL,3,CIs it the end of local police forces
OL,4,Cand will facial recognition be used
OL,5,Csafely?
OL,7,FPoliticians from the region give a
OL,8,Fcautious welcome to new technology
OL,9,Fwithin policing
OL,11,FThe biggest shake-up of policing in
OL,12,F200 years is due to include more than
OL,13,F#100million on new technology,
OL,14,Fincluding AI and facial recognition.
OL,16,FOn Around The House tonight (5
OL,17,FFebruary), two of our region's
OL,18,Fpoliticians give a cautious welcome
OL,19,Fbut say it must be handled with care.
