OL,3,CIs it the end of local police forces
OL,4,Cand will facial recognition be used
OL,5,Csafely?
OL,7,FJohn Lamont, Conservative MP for
OL,8,FBerwickshire, Roxburgh and Selkirk,
OL,9,Fsaid: "I do think technology has a
OL,10,Frole to play but it needs to be done
OL,11,Fin a way which protects people's
OL,12,Fliberties and people need to
OL,13,Funderstand how their information and
OL,14,Fhow they're being, basically,
OL,15,Fsurveillance - how the surveillance
OL,16,Fstate is going to be operating."
OL,18,FMeanwhile, crossbench peer Lord
OL,19,FInglewood said: "The other part of
OL,20,Fthis process is of course the way the
OL,21,Fcourts work.
