OL,3,CIs it the end of local police forces
OL,4,Cand will facial recognition be used
OL,5,Csafely?
OL,7,F"The courts have got to be able to
OL,8,Flook at these things critically so
OL,9,Fthat when judgement is made about
OL,10,Fevidence that's brought forward which
OL,11,Fhas been provided by this technology,
OL,12,Fthat they get it right."
OL,14,FMr Lamont and John Inglewood joined
OL,15,FPolitical Correspondent Tom Sheldrick
OL,16,Ffor February's edition of Around the
OL,17,FHouse which also sees the panel
OL,18,Fdiscuss WASP women comensation.
